# SCSS Styling Guide

## File Organization

```
_sass/
├── _variables.scss    # Colors, fonts, spacing, breakpoints
├── _base.scss         # Reset, typography, base elements
├── _components.scss   # Buttons, forms, cards, badges
├── _header.scss       # Site header and navigation
├── _footer.scss       # Site footer
├── _hero.scss         # Hero/banner sections
├── _sections.scss     # Homepage sections
├── _pages.scss        # Page-specific styles
└── _product.scss      # Product pages

assets/css/
└── main.scss          # Entry point (imports all partials)
```

